<item>
            <title>[KAFKA-1198] NullPointerException in describe topic</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/KAFKA-1198</link>
                <project id="12311720" key="KAFKA">Kafka</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;If topic is not specified, we get the following.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;bin/kafka-topics.sh --zookeeper localhost:2181 --describe&lt;br/&gt;
(Error while executing topic command,java.lang.NullPointerException)&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Also, list topic seems to always list all topics even when topics are specified.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
                <environment></environment>
        <key id="12687012">KAFKA-1198</key>
            <summary>NullPointerException in describe topic</summary>
                <type id="1" iconUrl="https://issues.apache.org/jira/secure/viewavatar?size=xsmall&amp;avatarId=21133&amp;avatarType=issuetype">Bug</type>
